Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.84,0:01:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can hear thunder rumbling in the distance.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.54,0:02:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whenever lightning approaches, I feel restless.
